  description="The Moose Studio Terms of Use governing a studio's participation in Moose, operated by Blubby Pty Ltd (trading as Moose Club). Covers Partnerships, the Moose Upgrade, Crossover Sessions, Upgrade Fees, reconciliation, conduct, liability and insurance."
